{"title":"阿妹上大学","authors":["李光云"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":3,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿妹上大学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李光云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿妹考进北京的大学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里常想山里的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像那些红嘴巴的燕子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贪恋故乡的小院"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而紧张的校园生活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改变了儿女情长的习惯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿妹生命的轨迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此充满挑战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老师春风扑面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开阔了远方的风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是将乡亲的嘱托"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揉进都市蓝蓝的天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打从离开故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一天的日程都排得很满"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只好抽空写封家书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将这里的繁华和喧闹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄给阿妈慢慢品尝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有执著的追求"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄然升起风帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载着亲人的祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遨游在知识的海洋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿妹此刻的心境"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铭刻着阿妈最初的心愿"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}